Project ModeEphemeral Mode <p>Uses the file directory when <code>go.mod</code> exists.</p> <pre><code>go run &lt;file.go&gt;
</code></pre> <p>Creates a temporary environment when <code>go.mod</code> is missing.</p> <pre><code>go mod init rightogo_temp_run
